            <td>Drain pump replacement or cleaning, clogged drain hose, pump filter blockage (front-load)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Leaking water</div><div class="repair-desc">Water on floor during or after cycle</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$320</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ parts if needed</div></td>
            <td>Door gasket (front-load), inlet hose connections, drain pump seal, tub seal</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Not starting / no power</div><div class="repair-desc">No response when starting, display dead</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$150&ndash;$300</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ parts if needed</div></td>
            <td>Door latch / lid switch, control board, thermal fuse, wiring harness</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><div class="repair-type">Shaking violently during spin</div><div class="repair-desc">Excessive vibration, machine walking across floor</div></td>
            <td><div class="price-labor">$160&ndash;$340</div><div class="price-parts-note">+ parts</div></td>
            <td>Drum bearing, shock absorbers, drum spider arm, leveling check. Also: shipping bolts still in place (no parts needed).</td>
          </tr>
