      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Why do you quote labor and parts separately?</div><div class="faq-a">Many LA repair companies use flat-rate BlueBook pricing that bundles labor and parts into a single number. A drain pump filter clog with no part needed should not cost the same as a drum bearing replacement. We quote separately so the price reflects your actual repair.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Are parts included in the quoted labor price?</div><div class="faq-a">No &mdash; all prices on this page are labor only. After diagnosis we quote the specific part needed as a separate line item. OEM parts wherever available. You see the full total before approving anything.</div></div>
