      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How much does Miele washer repair cost in Los Angeles?</div><div class="faq-a">Labor for Miele washer repair runs $280&ndash;$560+ depending on the failure. Miele uses proprietary European components at a premium price. Parts are quoted separately so you see exactly what the OEM Miele components cost.</div></div>
